{"tid":829062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇敢之盾聯演 美各軍種精銳盡出","createTime":"2018-09-20T06:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T06:12:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f675ab2fbab2a7a912219ebbf2c12403c7d69520","tid":829062,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.ydn.com.tw/ArticleFile/20180920/2018091922563430273.jpg?id=305745&amp;m=v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ydn.com.tw%2FArticleFile%2F20180920%2F2018091922563430273.jpg%3Fid%3D305745%26m%3Dv&h=d6fd3acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩年一度的「勇敢之盾」（Valiant Shield）聯演日前在關島與馬里亞納群島間的海域展開，除了「雷根號」航艦打擊群外，陸戰隊的F-35B戰機與海軍的陸基P-8A巡邏機也首度參與這場美國各軍種在西太平洋的最大規模聯戰演習。<br />\n<br />\n　來自美國陸海空三軍與陸戰隊各軍種的十餘艘艦艇、160架戰機與1.5萬官兵，在該區執行包括海上攔截、空戰攻防、情監偵、反潛與指管等各項操演課目，除了前述2款新戰機參演外，5月才抵達日本展開前進部署、具備最新版本神盾系統與飛彈防禦能力的驅逐艦「米利爾斯號」（DDG 69）也在參演序列中。<br />\n<br />\n　根據美國海軍學院新聞網（USNI）報導，這次「勇敢之盾」也會舉行「實彈擊沉演習」（SINKEX），這次的目標則是已經除役的兩棲登陸運輸艦「聖路易號」，但美國海軍並未宣布SINKEX相關細節。<br />\n<br />\n　今年稍早環太平洋演習的SINKEX，除了美國海軍空中、水面與水下的攻艦武器外，也納入美國陸軍與日本陸自的岸基反艦武器，引起廣泛矚目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ydn.com.tw/ArticleFile/20180920/2018091922563438084.JPG?id=305745&amp;m=v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ydn.com.tw%2FArticleFile%2F20180920%2F2018091922563438084.JPG%3Fid%3D305745%26m%3Dv&h=512a1e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ydn.com.tw/News/305745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ydn.com.tw%2FNews%2F305745&d=kThX8bkn0l1ex4g4vi8cwzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2185d552\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ydn.com.tw/News/305745</a>"},{"pid":"f9dc617fb8d31c8e96d3cc3e0b66b180b5d4e7a4","tid":829062,"uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">登上雷根號！　近距離看美軍備戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美軍雷根號航艦部署到東亞之後，首次讓台灣媒體登艦，TVBS是國際媒體當中獨家在勇敢之盾演習中成功登艦的媒體，帶您一起近距離觀看美軍的這場演習！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2018/09/19/20180919203215-c145fd99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F20180919203215-c145fd99.jpg&h=4129f77d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭乘美軍灰狗運輸機成功降落雷根號航空母艦。<br />\n<br />\n軍事記者相振為：「經過一小時的飛行，我們終於抵達雷根號航空母艦，現在就要踏上她的飛行甲板。」<br />\n<br />\n踏出機艙，待命中的大黃蜂戰機就矗立眼前，正在參與勇敢之盾演習的雷根號，國際媒體中只準許TVBS登艦，近距離看美軍備戰演練！<br />\n<br />\n軍事記者相振為：「您可以看到他們正在進行密集的起降作業，而我們是唯一成功登艦的國際媒體。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2018/09/19/20180919203221-bdcd0ab7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F20180919203221-bdcd0ab7.jpg&h=827c4538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從飛行甲板上、近在咫尺的距離，大黃蜂在我們的鏡頭前接連降落，它用機尾下方捕捉鉤勾住攔截索，讓戰機從高速瞬間完全停頓，看不過癮嗎，換個角度來看起飛！F-18透過蒸氣彈射器，時速瞬間從0加到300公里，噴射飛離甲板，這個超級大黃蜂戰機具備空對空、空對地跟反艦飛彈，還有極具威力的精準炸彈，是美軍重要的攻擊機種，何況雷根號航艦滿載可攜帶90架艦載機。<br />\n<br />\n軍事記者相振為：「這次我們TVBS獨家受邀到雷根號航艦來看他們的戰力有多強，我們來往他們的飛行甲板看，這邊停了密密麻麻的F-18大黃蜂戰機，這邊還有最新型號的E-2D預警機，是目前最新的飛機，接下來看到機尾編號500的這架是他們EA-18G咆哮者電戰機。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2018/09/19/20180919203227-cd4a38e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F20180919203227-cd4a38e2.jpg&h=808bc7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武器攻擊之外，具備電子作戰的EA-18G咆哮者電戰機，大方讓台灣媒體拍個夠，還有美軍最新的E-2D，「先進鷹眼」預警機首次在台灣媒體前亮相。<br />\n<br />\n聯合特遣隊指揮官KarlThomas：「我們對於在這個區域全部夥伴盟友跟朋友的承諾，我想提供了安全跟穩定，讓我們能同心協力彼此了解、確保這個世界上很重要的區域跟我們同在。」<br />\n<br />\n雷根號航艦不只參與勇敢之盾，更是第七艦隊中穩定朝鮮半島、台海跟南海的重要軍事武力，不論區域發生什麼變局，美軍都彰顯隨時做好準備的態勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/995497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F995497&d=kThX8bkn0l1ex4g4vi8cwzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7f3d1b8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/995497</a>"},{"pid":"ebee109846d05273905e7c76d2bd477ae61fb871","tid":829062,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:48:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">踏出機艙，待命中的大黃蜂戰機就矗立眼前，正在參與勇敢之盾演習的雷根號，國際媒體中只準許TVBS登艦，近距離看美軍備戰演練！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8829db6d865b058aa6b103aecc0bc0b3fb65e3","tid":829062,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc00628b230fb93a3c8762ccbf1f4e3c524282b","tid":829062,"uid":59283,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:50:54.000Z","msg":"根本唔係遼寧號對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b088f61989456146ea0fd002693f0fbc8c4245b1","tid":829062,"uid":818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"遼寧艦一出，誰與爭峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a533ad0db37e1b3f31836a2602edff43d7395ba0","tid":829062,"uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2017/07/08/20170708-011726_U1085_M298834_a5bc.png?itok=lgrzrGyb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F20170708-011726_U1085_M298834_a5bc.png%3Fitok%3DlgrzrGyb&h=78d4629c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ac74a39e55b912df63f4a2b2331650894bdc27d","tid":829062,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86a77d12cc4c48b8d96e6dae687c699e074dd08","tid":829062,"uid":55043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"航母戰鬥群淨係擺個陣出黎我係對面都即刻投降<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f12225f9d376f7674e9c329acff79b702e16e7","tid":829062,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c85182e18eeeb1977a7222f24dfa00d10449c3","tid":829062,"uid":10064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c86a77d12cc4c48b8d96e6dae687c699e074dd08","tid":829062,"uid":55043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"航母戰鬥群淨係擺個陣出黎我係對面都即刻投降<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T11:49:53.000Z","msg":"前題係打個時你有命睇到個陣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0990506bdb1c1e9b20d063051ea520e42cd8a035","tid":829062,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a533ad0db37e1b3f31836a2602edff43d7395ba0","tid":829062,"uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2017/07/08/20170708-011726_U1085_M298834_a5bc.png?itok=lgrzrGyb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F20170708-011726_U1085_M298834_a5bc.png%3Fitok%3DlgrzrGyb&h=78d4629c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"Pandarra Fog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那version"},{"pid":"a684af1818b50878bde7aca3